to work with json-server
------------------------
1) install json-server globally
		npm install -g json-server
2) start the json server by providing the json file which 
	is to be watched/which provides the data to the json-server
		json-server --watch src/assets/data/products.json
3) now json-server will listen on port 3000 and the url is 
		"http://localhost:3000/products"